@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.abs(0.84)
    v0 = (0.76 + ((v1 + 0.68 - v2 + 0.07) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.87)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (tmp / 0.37)
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.31 - v1 + 0.16)) + ((tmp + 0.79 + v1 + 0.38) + 0.16))
    tmp = (0.21 - (tmp * wp.sin(v0 + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
